## How this set is organised

- `features/<feature-slug>.md` — one file per user-facing feature, with user story, Gherkin acceptance criteria, and technical notes
- `features/<feature-slug>.feature` — executable Gherkin paired with the `.md` above

Cross-cutting artefacts at the root:
- `GAPS.md` — behaviour referenced in specs but not confirmable from code/docs
